{{Infobox Network | network_name = Hebei Television (HEBTV) | network_logo = [[Image:HebeiTV.png|200px|Hebei Television]] | country = [[People's Republic of China]] | network_type = [[Terrestrial television|Broadcast]] | available = | website = [http://www.hebtv.com/ www.hebtv.com/] | }}
'''Hebei Television''' (HEBTV), ({{zh|s=河北电视台|t=河北電視台|p=Héběi Diànshìtái}}) is a [[television network]] in [[Hebei]] province and all parts of the [[Beijing]] and [[Tianjin]] television viewing areas. Hebei Television also covers parts of [[Shandong]], [[Henan]] and [[Shaanxi]] provinces and the [[Inner Mongolia Autonomous Region]]. More than 120 million people enjoy access to the programs the television provides. Hebei Television has two channels, broadcasting 136 hours of programs and rebroadcasts programs from two other television stations. Besides, HEBTV broadcasts 2 hours of programs to North America each month via the Oriental Satellite Television. <ref>[http://www.chinaculture.org/gb/en_aboutchina/2003-09/24/content_23694.htm www.chinaculture.org/]</ref>
==Channels== *[[HEBTV-1]]- A comprehensive channel, which broadcasts news, programs in the arts, movies and plays ** Its major programs are Hebei News Broadcast (Hebei Xinwen Lianbo), [[HEBTV Economy Watch|Economy Watch]] (Jingji Guancha), [[HEBTV Society Focus|Society Focus]] (Shehui Shidian), [[HEBTV Movie World|Movie World]] (Dianying Da Shijie) and [[HEBTV Sports Circle|Sports Circle]] (Titan Neiwai). *[[HEBTV-2]]- Focuses on the economy ** It broadcasts major programs such as [[HEBTV Economy Watch|Economy Watch]] (Jingji Guancha), [[HEBTV Economy Express|Economy Express]] (Jingji Chuanzhen), [[HEBTV Securities Today|Securities Today]] (Jinri Zhengquan) and [[HEBTV Economy Life|Economy Life]] (Jingji Shenghuo). * [[HEBTV-3]] (HEBTV-都市) &ndash; City ** Major programs: City Life (Dushi Shenghuo), Sports News (Tiyu Xinwen) * [[HEBTV-4]] (HEBTV-影视) &ndash; Movie & Television ** Major Programs: Circulation of Entertainment (Ying shi quan), Movie World (Ying shi da shi jie), Movie & TV Dictionary (Ying shi bao dian) * [[HEBTV-5]] (HEBTV-少儿科教) &ndash; Children & Education ** Major Programs: Military Files (Jun shi dang an), Growing (Cheng zhang), Children World (Shao er tian di), SF Movie Review (Kehuan yingshi shangxi) * [[HEBTV-6]] (HEBTV-公共) &ndash; Public ** Major Programs: Happy 50 mins (Kuaile 50 fen), Law Time (Fazhi tian di), Chatroom (Liao tian shi) * [[HEBTV-Farmer]] (HEBTV-农民) &ndash; Farmer & Agriculture ** Major Programs: San nong zui qian xian
The television station has three studios. Both the 800-square-meter and 400-square-meter studios are equipped with digital devices.
